    "description": "This carb smart recipe replaces half the white rice for cauliflower rice. Summer really is the season to spotlight incredible fruit and veg. For this dish, you'll serve smoky grilled tomatoes with golden curried chicken thighs and spinach rice. Drizzle the spicy mango dressing over to serve.",
